{"tid":2370701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員余俊鑫猥褻6名女童認罪候判 求情指14歲女童主動擁抱要求送回家 1月27日判刑","createTime":"2021-01-18T08:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T10:21:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2dffe76b978e0f6f71e69e08515b6150932e67","tid":2370701,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:21:31.000Z","msg":"現停職的毒品調查科警員於2017年至2018年間，多次在梯間及公園非禮和與女童非法性交等，被控非禮、與16歲以下女童非法性交等共12項控罪，受害女童年齡介乎11至14歲。被告早前承認全部控罪，辯方今在區域法院求情稱，其中一名與被告性交的14歲女童，曾主動擁抱被告及要被吿送她回家，因而向被告發出錯誤訊息。祁士偉法官將判刑押後至本月27日。<br />\n<br />\n35歲被告余俊鑫承認於2017至2018年，在天水圍某停車場梯間、秀茂坪某屋邨梯間及黃大仙某公園，5度向4名16歲以下女童X、Y、A和B作出猥褻行為；於2018年4月至7月間，2度在黃大仙某公園和石門某屋邨梯間，與16歲以下女童B和C非法性交；於2018年6月6日在香港於其智能電話內，管有兒童色情物品，即28張兒童色情相片。<br />\n<br />\n法庭早前為被告索取了背景及心理報告。辯方今引述報告內容稱，被告對犯案的深切反省及感到後悔，對涉案女童受到傷害及要家人擔心感到內疚。還押2年以來，被告尋求心理治療，目前正在康復中。辯方又稱，被告並無使用暴力，事件中無人受傷，加上被告主動認罪，避免涉案6名女童上庭作供，希望法庭以此為減刑因素。<br />\n<br />\n被告曾與女童B和C非法性交，辯方對此求情謂，被告與女童B建立了情侶關係，並非單純誘使B與他性交。女童C在事發當晚則主動擁抱被告，被告本來已經離開，但C主動聯絡被告，要被告送她回家，令被告因而誤會，事件並沒有預謀。而且，C事後繼續交男朋友，顯示她仍願意接受新關係。"},{"pid":"278ed36af20356dd70b020a41414e7ec5abbcf81","tid":2370701,"uid":78243,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"留名睇判社會服務令"},{"pid":"8db0d41d219a267f0a0cbaf760d3360978ec168f","tid":2370701,"uid":3086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"坐兩三個禮拜就無事<br />\n出黎再屌過"},{"pid":"bd185a256c8a24db6e8dc58b15869bed5d580b62","tid":2370701,"uid":388108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"278ed36af20356dd70b020a41414e7ec5abbcf81","tid":2370701,"uid":78243,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"留名睇判社會服務令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"話唔定入去男女童院做「社會服務令」呢"},{"pid":"9874cceb82bb4e9e23a707a4c33ecc5f3852a9d2","tid":2370701,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"做警察份內事都拉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d5ed3c18e700234f47f3c40d8c3308b3d1a348","tid":2370701,"uid":120660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"哇屌你老母<br />\n仲要賴返個細路女轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e271395ede6d64798562ecbddb9b07b115e1c24","tid":2370701,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2efbd28281a9be0ae2acf6289d267d89a9701d","tid":2370701,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d5ed3c18e700234f47f3c40d8c3308b3d1a348","tid":2370701,"uid":120660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"哇屌你老母<br />\n仲要賴返個細路女轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcce9f70cd0f87b345f328e581c574299ae9965","tid":2370701,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:36:20.000Z","msg":"訓斥"},{"pid":"39f8ca7aa4ae716640d3a3e6ff93ecfbcccef477","tid":2370701,"uid":76804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b4d5ed3c18e700234f47f3c40d8c3308b3d1a348","tid":2370701,"uid":120660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"哇屌你老母<br />\n仲要賴返個細路女轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"佢地有邊次唔係blame the victim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888fc698ef3f2cc64c7d3046b55c018bae75da8d","tid":2370701,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"被告事發後已被停職，他早前兩項向 16 歲以下女童作出猥褻行為、一項管有兒童色情物品、三項非禮及兩項與 16 歲以下女童非法性交罪，指他於 2017 年 12 月至 2018 年 7 月犯案，共涉及 6 名年齡介乎 11 至 14 歲女童A、B、C、X、Y及Z。<br />\n<br />\n男警專向未成年少女埋手 <br />\n<br />\n案情顯示，被告專門向未成年少女埋手。他透過社交媒體 Intagram及 Facebook 結識受害女童後，向當中 3 名女童展開追求，不斷表達愛意，並以「老公、老婆」相稱，其後更上下其手，大肆非禮。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-6-%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B0%E5%83%85-11-%E6%AD%B2-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85-%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%93%81%E6%8A%B1%E6%88%96%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%88-%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%258C%25A5%25E8%25A4%25BB-6-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E5%2583%2585-11-%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2583%2585-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%2593%2581%25E6%258A%25B1%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BA%2588-%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=bb702ac8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%258C%25A5%25E8%25A4%25BB-6-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E5%2583%2585-11-%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2583%2585-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%2593%2581%25E6%258A%25B1%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BA%2588-%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF%2F&h=5838e5e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-6-%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B0%E5%83%85-11-%E6%AD%B2-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85-%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%93%81%E6%8A%B1%E6%88%96%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%88-%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF/</a>"},{"pid":"89d20fdcf8da7dbe4604fd2f85438212791b8298","tid":2370701,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:12:38.000Z","msg":"忠誠勇毅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc2ed69c4dc0da8c78c15b1864a4f32ab2758da","tid":2370701,"uid":278152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c6b370685f5d2b421e2b891019d5d7463b83c6","tid":2370701,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"阿sir衰11唔使你教"},{"pid":"5e9ae3c98c116377a4ea9c292502d371d36a48ba","tid":2370701,"uid":364767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"『主動擁抱』就會建立情侶關係？ 咁.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E8%91%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F2%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E8%2591%25A3%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF.jpg&h=248ba0a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f442de262577f70f12b61701686bb1c5ca5537ea","tid":2370701,"uid":62710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:21:21.000Z","msg":"明顯係女童故意設局引誘陷害<br />\n應該用阻差辦公拉埋幾個女童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d1ee88df16a3b628b201c535cca26536b1a61f","tid":2370701,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"淫警社交媒體獵女童「起雙飛」迫性交 稱及早認罪<strong><span class=\"red\">求多於三分一減刑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n毒品調查科警員利用facebook及instagram等社交媒體，以未成年女童作目標，獻上甜言蜜語，聲稱願跟女童成為情侶，並以「老公老婆」相稱，卻趁見面時加以侵犯，甚至迫誘女童在公園性交，並曾找來未成年兼職女友「起雙飛」，先後狎玩六女童。一度被控強姦的警員早前在區域法院承認非禮等八項罪名，法官祁士偉今聽取求情時主動提出，被告擔任警隊工作是否影響判刑。辯方大狀則指被告認罪，免卻女生上庭作供所造成的影響，且有20封嘉許信，要求法庭給予「多於三分一」的減刑。案件押後至本月27日判刑，被告繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/QJZQBFJMN5EW5IGGSIUBJ6KOTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FQJZQBFJMN5EW5IGGSIUBJ6KOTM%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=7b5913af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FQJZQBFJMN5EW5IGGSIUBJ6KOTM%2F&h=90f04c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/QJZQBFJMN5EW5IGGSIUBJ6KOTM/</a>"},{"pid":"ec81d07cdcab1754f97d5edc529a092df3093ae7","tid":2370701,"uid":249722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cd881d9ea6bf01791f1d1a3bd89e0df2a02b91","tid":2370701,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"叫拜登寫求情信"},{"pid":"71f348a8e812058b18af09f79842d64091baa3c9","tid":2370701,"uid":263200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278ed36af20356dd70b020a41414e7ec5abbcf81","tid":2370701,"uid":78243,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T